uiEntry.title: assigned_character
uiEntry.script:
function ManageSelection( card, click_up )
if click_up then
UIComponent( Component.Root() ):LuaCall( "ShowUnitInfoCharacterInfo", UIComponent( card ):LuaCall( "ItemAddress" ) )
end
end
